Pontoscolex (P.) pydanieli spec. nov. (Oligochaeta, Glossoscolecidae) and its Parasite Pessoaella pontoscolecis gen. nov., spec. nov. (Eugregarinida, Aikinetocystidae)Pontoscolex (P.) pydanieli; spec. nov., described from Brazil, Rondonia, has unusual organization of the septa and holonephridia with a bunch of funnels. Its coelomic parasite, Pessoaella pontoscolecis; gen. nov., spec, nov., has branches with wide and simple endings.